TerrariaTrees.name: TerrariaTrees

deaths.deathMessage: TerrariaTrees was blown up by Creeper

TerrariaTrees.taskDescription: You are now a weeping angel until the end of the session. If you're aware that someone is looking at you, you are not allowed to move until they stop looking at you.

scarwe.name: scarwe

deaths.deathMessage: scarwe was slain by Piglin Brute
scarwe fell from a high place

scarwe.taskDescription: Use a redstone contraption to damage another player. You can't hit them with a redstone item, it must be some kind of trap or machine.

RavingRaven43453.name: RavingRaven43453

deaths.deathMessage: RavingRaven43453 was slain by Piglin Brute
RavingRaven43453 was slain by scarwe using §f[§oScarlett Slayer§f]

RavingRaven43453.taskDescription: You are now MrKoolBuckzz's assassin. Brew or purchase an invisibility potion and kill them without them figuring out who you are. If you're figured out, you fail the task.

OrcaHedral.name: OrcaHedral

deaths.deathMessage: OrcaHedral tried to swim in lava

OrcaHedral.taskDescription: Meow once during a conversation without being called out/someone esle meowing. If called out, try again in a different conversation (preferably with other players).

Spectral_Blue.name: Spectral_Blue
Spectral_Blue.taskDescription: Meet {player} and build a place to perform a stand-up comedy event near spawn, in front of at least 3 players. Zylphys must write every joke without telling the performer what they are, and the performer must then perform them live, completely blind.

Aryid.name: Aryid
Aryid.taskDescription: Back seat __waffle's game for the next 10 minutes. If they call you out, move onto another player, for a maximum of 3 attempts before failure.

OperationDusty.name: OperationDusty

deaths.deathMessage: OperationDusty was doomed to fall by RavingRaven43453

OperationDusty.taskDescription: Move 5 people's chests at least once. If someone calls you out, that person doesn't count.

Daisyrebelle.name: Daisyrebelle
Daisyrebelle.taskDescription: [SL] Make a pun at every opportunity during a conversation. You must make at least 3 successful puns within a 5 minute time-span.

Invictus_Delta.name: Invictus_Delta
Invictus_Delta.taskDescription: You must participate in a build battle against scarwe, for any build of your choice. Get some players to judge the builds and the loser fails the task.

koopafan69.name: koopafan69
koopafan69.taskDescription: Give 3 nonsense compliments to 3 separate players, and get them to thank you. For example, stare at them longingly and say "has anyone ever told you that you have 2 eyes?".

Nitura.name: Nitura

deaths.deathMessage: Nitura fell from a high place

Nitura.taskDescription: Say a line/lyric from Captain Sparklez's "Revenge" in at least 3 different conversations. Each line/lyric must be different for each conversation. If someone calls you out, that conversation doesn't count.

Zylphys.name: Zylphys
Zylphys.taskDescription: [SL] Call people anything other than their name/username for the next hour.

FizzyKinkajou49.name: FizzyKinkajou49
FizzyKinkajou49.taskDescription: [SL] Be Aryid's hype person for the next 30 minutes and don't get called out. If you get called out, switch to any other player and reset the timer, or fail the task (your choice).

Tal_Doesnt_Exist.name: Tal_Doesnt_Exist
Tal_Doesnt_Exist.taskDescription: Tell 3 jokes where the punchline is complete nonsense, tricking players into laughing at something they don't understand, and don't get called out. If you get called out, that joke doesn't count.

Spectralwraith.name: Spectralwraith

deaths.deathMessage: Spectralwraith was burned to a crisp while fighting scarwe

Spectralwraith.taskDescription: For the next hour and a half, you are a serial yapper. Go on random tangents, talk way too much and take control of every conversation by telling random and irrelevant stories.

deaths.deathMessage: Spicy_Trombone fell from a high place

flywiththenight.name: flywiththenight
flywiththenight.taskDescription: Steal 4 people's beds without being caught and make a shrine out of them. If you're caught, you fail the task.

Yoavis.name: Yoavis
Yoavis.taskDescription: Go mining with a partner, and excitedly call them over at least 3 times for a big ore find. When they arrive and see nothing, blame a creeper explosion for the missing ore.

MrKoolBuckzz.name: MrKoolBuckzz
MrKoolBuckzz.taskDescription: [SL] Call people anything other than their name/username for the next hour.

SanguisAureus.name: SanguisAureus

deaths.deathMessage: SanguisAureus was slain by scarwe using §f[§oScarlett Slayer§f]

SanguisAureus.taskDescription: Ask someone why Keanu is marked as Treasurer on the Discord when he's clearly President. You win when someone tells you the correct answer (stupid guild stuff).

jjorj.name: jjorj
jjorj.taskDescription: Two people will soon announce that they are running against each other for the position of president in the server. Your task is to build a voting booth and convince them to use it to count the votes. You fail if they refuse to use it for the election.

Whitbee.name: Whitbee
Whitbee.taskDescription: Convince someone that you have the same task as them.

__waffle.name: __waffle
__waffle.taskDescription: Place as many excess blocks as you can around someone's base without them noticing while you're talking to them. You succeed if you place a minimum of 20 blocks. If you're caught, move on to a different player.
